README - Siddharth Chhatbar

In this program user can visualize in-place sorting algorithms.
There are currently 2 alogrithms, Bubble Sort and Insertion Sort.
User can press 'B' for bubble sort and 'I' for insertion sort.
User can choose to sort the ramdomly generated numbers in ascending and descending order.
User can press 'A' to sort in ascending order and 'D' to sort in descending order.
'R' can be pressend anytime, evend during the algorithm runtime to reset the program.
Pressing spacebar will start sorting.